sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.DBSS_Controller</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description>Calculate DBSS Values</description><name>DBSS_Controller</name><script><![CDATA[var DBSS_Controller = Class.create();

DBSS_Controller.prototype = {
	
	initialize: function() {
	},
	
	// Calculate a value with summary table writer
	// P1: pSSName: Name of summary set
	// P2: pTable: Name of table
	// P3: pField: Name of catagory field
	// P4: pQuery: Query-String
	// P5: pValue: Value of the category
	// Result: percentage of the value
	calculateSummaryValue: function(pSSName, pTable, pField, pQuery, pValue) {
		var res = 0.0;
		
		var grSS = new GlideRecord('sys_report_summary');
		grSS.addQuery('title',pSSName);
		grSS.deleteMultiple();
		
		var summarySet = new SummaryTableWriter(pTable, pField);
		summarySet.setTitle(pSSName);
		summarySet.setQuery(pQuery);
		summarySet.generate();
		
		// Setzen des Indikatorwertes
		grSS = new GlideRecord('sys_report_summary');
		if (grSS.get('title',pSSName))
			{
			//gs.log('Refresh Summary ' + pSSName + ' SSet found');
			// Read Line with Priority 1
			var grSSline = new GlideRecord('sys_report_summary_line');
			grSSline.addQuery('summary', grSS.sys_id);
			grSSline.addQuery('category', pValue);
			grSSline.query();
			if (grSSline.next())
				{
				res = grSSline.percent;
			}
		}
		return res;
	},
	
	_calculateValue: function(pSSName, pTable, pField, pL1Name) {
		
		var grSS = new GlideRecord('sys_report_summary');
		grSS.addQuery('title',pSSName);
		grSS.deleteMultiple();
		
		var summarySet = new SummaryTableWriter(pTable, pField);
		summarySet.setTitle(pSSName);
		summarySet.setQuery("active=true");
		summarySet.generate();
		
		// Setzen des Indikatorwertes
		grSS = new GlideRecord('sys_report_summary');
		if (grSS.get('title',pSSName))
			{
			//gs.log('Refresh Summary ' + pSSName + ' SSet found');
			var grSSline = new GlideRecord('sys_report_summary_line');
			grSSline.addQuery('summary', grSS.sys_id);
			grSSline.addQuery('category','1');
			grSSline.query();
			if (grSSline.next())
				{
				//gs.log('Refresh Summary "DBSS_Active Problems by Priority" SS-Line found');
				var grDBSSl1 = new GlideRecord('u_dbss_level1');
				if (grDBSSl1.get('u_name', pL1Name))
					{
					grDBSSl1.u_current_value = grSSline.percent;
					grDBSSl1.update();
					gs.log('Refresh Summary ' + pSSName + ' done');
					
				}
			}
		}
	},
	
	_refreshLevel2Sets: function () {
		gs.log('DBSS: Start Refresh Level 2');
		
		var grDBSSl2 = new GlideRecord('u_dbss_level2');
		var praefixSS = 'DBSS_';
		
		grDBSSl2.query();
		while (grDBSSl2.next())
			{
			var nameSS = praefixSS + grDBSSl2.u_name;
			var grSS = new GlideRecord('sys_report_summary');
			grSS.addQuery('title',nameSS);
			grSS.deleteMultiple();
			
			var summarySet = new SummaryTableWriter(grDBSSl2.u_table, grDBSSl2.u_category_field);
			summarySet.setTitle(nameSS);
			if (!grDBSSl2.u_filter.nil()) {
				summarySet.setQuery(grDBSSl2.u_filter);
			}
			summarySet.generate();
			
			var grSSr = new GlideRecord('sys_report_summary');
			if (grSSr.get('title',nameSS))
				{
				grDBSSl2.u_summaryset = grSSr.sys_id;
				grDBSSl2.update();
				gs.log('Level 2 /' + grDBSSl2.u_name + ' refreshed');
			}
			
		}
	},
	
	refresh: function() {
		var ssName2 = 'DBSS_Active Incidents by Category';
		
		// Summary "DBSS_Active Incidents by Priority"
		gs.log('Refresh Summary DBSS started');
		
		this._calculateValue('DBSS_Active Incidents by Priority', 'incident', 'priority', 'High Prio Incidents');
		this._calculateValue('DBSS_Active Problems by Priority', 'problem', 'priority', 'High Prio Problems');
		this._calculateValue('DBSS_Active Changes by Priority', 'change_request', 'priority', 'High Prio Changes');
		
		this._refreshLevel2Sets();
		
		gs.log('Refresh Summary DBSS done');
	},
	
	type: 'DBSS_Controller'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>gbt_ext</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2013-10-25 08:19:00</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>da74337eb0e0d100eb79fd0317dfe8ea</sys_id><sys_mod_count>39</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DBSS_Controller</sys_name><sys_package display_value="gbe_dbas" source="NULL">b9549fdec8acd940ab00a95567e2ff0d</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="gbe_dbas">b9549fdec8acd940ab00a95567e2ff0d</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_da74337eb0e0d100eb79fd0317dfe8ea</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin_gbernuetz</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-01-30 16:02:03</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
